data.description: Located in the prestigious North Gwinnett School district. This beautiful 2 story home features vaulted ceilings with lots of natural light. The eat in kitchen has a view to the living room which is easy for entertaining. The basement is stubbed for a bathroom and ready for you to make it your own.  3 bedrooms including the Master are located on the upper level and features walk in closets. One bedroom is located on the  main level with access to the full bath and can double as an office. The home is positioned on a culdesac with a  completely fenced in backyard. This tight nit community neighborhood has convenient access to the walking trails connecting you to the Greenway and Downtown Suwanee. Hurry this beauty won't last long!!
